  <content>Example:

##{{{{{kanbanboard selection="space" space="TaskManager" /}}}}}##

* ##selection## [optional, default=all] select the method to display tasks ##all##, ##user##, ##space## or ##project##)
* ##user## [optional, default=$xcontext.userReference] define the user for method ##selection="user"##
* ##space## [optional, default=TaskManager] define the space for method ##selection="space"##
* ##project## [optional, default=] define the project for method ##selection="project"##

Example:

{{kanbanboard selection="space" space="TaskManager"/}}</content>
